title: RegularStreet
---
<<set_enabled_in_unity "BakerAudioFire" true>>
<<set_enabled_in_unity "BakerAudio" false>>
Baker: "Where do you think you're going with that bread? You have to pay for that!" #line:0d3680c 
Woman: "Please sir, me and my children, we are starving. I can't afford anything, my husband died fighting for this kingdom." #line:0bbc278 
Baker: "Look lady i understand your situation, but were all struggeling to make ends meet here so you can't just go around stealing things" #line:0c589e9 
Woman: "Please, i am willing to do anything, just let me get this bread to my children" #line:097c719 
Baker: "Lady..." #line:0087e24 

Witch: "So this is how you treat your subjects? This widow is starving and desperate. My sweet regent, aren't you going to intervene?" #line:0399a4b 
===

title: Intervene
---
Baker: "Ah hello my regent, why do you grace us with your presence today"  #line:018a23e 
Regent: "I overheared your commotion and decided to check it out" #line:02d8cf0 
Woman: "My regent... there's no reason for you to intervene with such a small issue. The baker and I have this sorted.?" #line:0decc37 
-> Don't Worry I understand #line:05fc78b 
    Regent: "Don't worry, i understand. Here is some money so that you can pay this kind baker over here. It should be enough to get you back up your feet and find a job so that you can support your kids" #line:072d637 
    Woman: "My regent. i can't-" #line:0af5b34 
    Regent: "You can, and you will. You are my subject and are a widow because of my wars. I am sorry for what happened to your husband, take this money, its the least i could do. " #line:0126eb8 
    Woman: "My regent, thank you, thank you so much" #line:07671d4 
    <<set $reputation to $reputation + 25>>
    <<set $payedWoman to true>>
    <<walk_to "Woman" "MomTalk" 0 false>>
    <<wait 2>>
    <<set_enabled_in_unity "BakerAudioFire" false>>
    <<set_enabled_in_unity "BakerAudio" true>>
-> Silence #line:0ff6115 
    Regent: "Silence, I saw what happened, if you really were starving you would be spending your time finding a job instead of stealing from others" #line:03f7b8f 
    Woman: "You're right my regent, my apologies. It's just that-" #line:0db8321 
    Regent: "I heared your excuses, you should be lucky i don't throw you into jail with that mentality, now go ahead and apologise to the baker and leave. " #line:0e26352 
        <<walk_to "Woman" "MomTalk" 0 false>>
    Baker: "My regent was that really necessary? She is starving and doesn't know what to do" #line:047496c 
    Regent: "So you would want me to condone stealing instead?" #line:01b361c 
    Baker: "Well no ofcourse not, my apologies my regent." #line:09c8e16 
    <<set $reputation to $reputation - 25>>
    <<wait 2>>
    <<set_enabled_in_unity "BakerAudioFire" false>>
    <<set_enabled_in_unity "BakerAudio" true>>
===

title: FightingClub
---
Woman: "My son haven't I told you not to go there? It's dangerous, you could get killed" #line:00f2d78 
Son: "Mother you know we have to, the taxes are too high and we can't afford food anymore. #line:0eb22a2 
Son: I can't have my siblings become beggars. " #line:0a83248 
Witch: "My my, my sweet regent. This one has a lot of potential. #line:09f007c 
Witch: I can basically see the mana radiating off of him... interesting" #line:08753de 
-> "What caused these scars young one?"" #line:0bce6a6 
    <<if $payedWoman == true>>
        Woman: "Hello my regent, thank you again for helping me. #line:09a09b8 
        Woman: My son wanted to help get food and went to the fightclub nearby to get money" #line:0dae066 
        Son: "Mother no, also what are you talking about?" #line:0cb1e50 
        Woman: "Our regent gave us some money to get back up on our feet. You dont have to fight anymore" #line:04e1b45 
        Son: "Mother, just because we now have money doesn't mean that you can just talk about the fightclub in front of the regent. #line:01cebfe 
        son: Those people still need their money. The club is illigal, what if they get caught" #line:0444994 
