            Regent: "I noticed that you have great potential to be a mage.  I want you to be a mage of my court. Some of the best mages in this kingdom will teach you everything."
            Regent: "In exchange, you are under my control you will not have it easy, but you will be great."  #line:0e7dd30 
            Boy: "Really? Thank you so much my regent, I will work hard I promise!"   #line:0c43a94 
            This will be the end for now             #line:0d09fd5 
