title: heroesParty
---
<<set_enabled_in_unity "SmithBonk" false>>
Regent: "What is going on here" #line:0107e39 
Smith: "My regent-" #line:0ffb971 
Party leader: "So you're the noble regent of this city, let me introduce myself." #line:03ae300 
Epheulia: "My name is Epheulia and I am the leader of this party." #line:0ab0309 
Epheulia: "You see the smith over here he... owes us something and doesn't want to pay it back." #line:0f103db 
Smith: "My regent, this isn't true. They are trying to use their fame to get my finest sword for free." #line:04f0346 
Witch: "My my, my sweet regent, this would be the perfect time to introduce these heroes here to your kingdom. #line:0fc3170 
Witch: I bet these people could be very useful... if you play your cards right " #line:080d6ac 
->"I'll give you the reward, but-" #line:0a7849c 
    Regent: "Thank you fine heroes for saving my kingdom and slaying the dragon nearby, I will reward you for this heroic deed." #line:044ee7c 
    Regent: "Though i do ask you not to make trouble for my subjects again. Take this money and pay the Smith, keep the rest as a reward." #line:03c78e7 
    Smith: "Thank you my regent" #line:05ec022 
->"This is NOT how we handle things" #line:0b96f83 
    Regent: "This is not how we handle things in this kingdom. I suggest you learn some respect before you anger the wrong person. #line:0c6b22c 
    Regent: Now about the reward you were supposed to get.. Half of that will go to the Smith you just threathened, take this as a lesson and continue on your way." #line:0f26799 
    Epheulia: "Thank you for this... lesson. It will be of great use to us in the nearby future" #line:05664c0 
    Party member: "But Epheulia they just-" #line:007797e 
    Epheulia: "Quiet, the regent has spoken, let us be on our way then." #line:02b1364 
-> Ignore it #line:0ecfeea 
    Regent: "I will not waste my time on this sorry excuse of a party without manners. Find a solution yourself" #line:0c4ec73 
