title: Uprise
---
Epheulia: Dear Citizens, we are the group that recently defeated a dragon near this kingdom and saved you all. #line:0780025 
<<if $reputation > 50>>
Epheulia: Your regent, instead of rewarding us for our hard work, punished us and took away half of our intended reward #line:072942d 
-> "Epheulia didn't I tell you not to cause trouble?" #line:009c63d 
    Regent: Epheulia, didn't I tell you just now not to cause trouble?  #line:069b8d6 
    Regent: "I thought I was very clear, sadly it seems like you don't understand. In this kingdom my people are first. #line:0e0c742 
    Regent:  "You tried to steal from the smith. Be glad I still gave you half of your reward after this distastefull behaviour. " #line:02fb83f 
    Epheulia: "I will say I am quite dissapointed in you regent, I came here wanting to be your friend..." #line:0502405 
    Epheulia: "but all I got was this saddening distrust. I don't even know what i did to deserve this" #line:01dfa43 
    <<set $reputation to $reputation + 10>>
    ->"You know exactly what you did" #line:0404bcd 
        Regent: "Oh Epheulia you know exactly what you did to deserve this." #line:0600a76 
        Regent: "Though i would love to play this game with you, I have more important matters to attent to." #line:0fd752b 
        Regent: "My guards here will show you out of my kingdom" #line:03c4188 
        Epheulia: "Thats too bad, I would have loved to play games with you" #line:0d23d01 
        Regent: "My dear, i am the regent of this kingdom. I don't have any time for your foolish games," #line:0f4b29c 
        Regent: "now please get out of my sight so that I can continue with my business" #line:001277b 
        Party member: "Epheulia tell the regent about- " #line:0e349a0 
        Epheulia: "That's enough from you, we'll be going now regent, thank you for your hospitility" #line:0eb730c 
        This will be the end for now #line:0748fb3 
    ->"Oh I'm sorry dear, did I misunderstand?" #line:0ba95df 
        Regent: "Oh I am so sorry my dear, did I merely misunderstand your past interactions?" #line:0abdafe 
        Regent: "Where you tried to rob one of my subjects?" #line:0031cb0 
        Regent: "Or was it just now where you tried to twist the situation against me and this fair smith?" #line:0d7c903 
        Regent: "Do explain to me Epheulia where exactly I misunderstood your intents?"  #line:0033ed7 
        Epheulia: "My regent, I just wanted to be your friend." #line:0aa11e2 
        Epheulia: "I even have some information I am willing to share with you as a token of my friendship." #line:0daf887 
        Regent: "Go on..." #line:03d2c40 
        Epheulia: "My regent, if only you were aware of what was going on in your kingdom..." #line:09570c3 
        Epheulia: "you see there is a fightclub just down the road from here. #line:03bd658 
        Epheulia: "I guess you need to start paying some attention your majesty" #line:0034c0a 
        Epheulia: "For now we'll be going, goodluck with that though!" #line:07afbb7 
        This will be the end for now #line:0ee6643 
-> "Now now Smith, that's enough" #line:042890f 
    Regent: "Now now smith, that is enough" #line:00a2914 
    Regent: "These heroes, just because they have misunderstood the situation, doesn't make them theves" #line:02b10ac 
    Smith: But my regent- #line:025072c 
    Regent: I have heared enough smith, you can go.  #line:09dea0b 
    <<set $reputation to $reputation- 10>>
    Regent: Now my dear subjects, let me explain the situation. #line:0f5f333 
    Regent: These lovely heroes weren't acustomed to our rules yet. #line:0d12a29 
    Regent: The situation was resolved though i believe they have misunderstood my intentions. #line:0ca3bc7 
    Regent: My apologies for that Epheulia #line:0c14b9c 
    party member: But that isn't-  #line:0fedf41 
    Epheulia: Thank you for clearing this up with us dear regent, now is there a chance we could talk?  #line:0de372d 
    This will be the end for now #line:0408ade 
    


<<elseif $reputation < 50 >>
Epheulia: "Your regent, instead of rewarding us for our hard work disrespected and ignored us" #line:0477a25 
