title: hearThemOut
---
Regent: "I suppose you have a point there. So if i understand you were robbing the smith?" #line:09a477b 
    Epheulia: "Not exactly, we just took what was ours, your kingdom owes us for defending you so we want our reward." #line:0144dac 
    -> "Do you really think you deserve a reward after this?" #line:01aae38 
        Regent: "I do not condone this kind of behaviour. People like you do not deserve rewards, be lucky I don't throw you in jail." #line:0c55016 
        Epheulia: "Your mercy is appriciated regent, we shall take our leave now" #line:071a432 
        This will be the end for now #line:0baec1c 
    -> "You will get your reward, just leave my subjects alone" #line:0321874 
        Regent: "I will grand you a reward though this behaviour will not go unpunished. You will not only apologise to the smith but also give him what you owe him using your reward." #line:0a72c54 
        Epheulia: "Thank you regent for making the right decision." #line:0cfab70 
        Epheulia: "Now let me offer you something in return as a token of friendship" #line:0633d6f 
        Epheulia: "You see my regent, a little birdy told me about something quite interesting." #line:0ed566d 
        Epheulia: "You see my regent did you know that there is quite the sensational fightclub in town, all adventurers speak of it." #line:01a48e3 
     -> "Guards take these thieves away" #line:0aa53ec 
        Regent: "You just confessed to stealing. Guards take these thieves away" #line:0f94a43 
        Epheulia: "Oh your majesty I fear you're making a grave mistake, but what's done is done" #line:0acfbbc 
        Party member: "But Epheulia they can't just do this to us, we are- " #line:024e583 
        Epheulia: "Shut it, the regent has spoken so we'll listen" #line:0973e24 
        Witch: "Oh my, sweet regent. This choice, though fair, will give you some quite powerful enemies." #line:0bbc4b1 
        This will be the end for now #line:0629892 
